## 8. RESPONSIVE DESIGN

### Breakpoints

|Device     |Min Width|Max Width|Layout                                     |
|-----------|---------|---------|-------------------------------------------|
|**Mobile** |â€”        |767px    |1 colonne, navigation bottom bar           |
|**Tablet** |768px    |1023px   |2 colonnes, navigation side bar optionnelle|
|**Desktop**|1024px   |â€”        |3 colonnes, navigation side bar fixe       |

### RÃ¨gles Responsive

**Mobile First**  
Tous les styles de base sont pour mobile. On ajoute progressivement pour Ã©crans plus grands.

```css
/* Base (Mobile) */
.grid {
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
}

/* Tablet */
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
}

/* Desktop */
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  }
}
```

