## 9. NAVIGATION & STRUCTURE Dâ€™Ã‰CRAN

### Bottom Navigation Bar (Mobile)

**Position :** Fixe en bas, toujours visible  
**Height :** 64px + safe-area-inset-bottom  
**Items :** 4 max (Dashboard, Groupes, Ã‰vÃ©nements, Profil)

```css
.bottom-nav {
  position: fixed;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 64px;
  background: #FFFFFF;
  box-shadow: 0px -2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-around;
  align-items: center;
  padding-bottom: env(safe-area-inset-bottom);
  z-index: 1000;
}

.nav-item {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 4px;
  color: #B2BEC3;
  transition: color 0.2s ease;
}

.nav-item.active {
  color: #FF6B6B;
}

.nav-item.active .icon {
  transform: scale(1.1);
}
```

### Side Navigation (Desktop)

**Width :** 240px fixe  
**Position :** Fixed left  
**Contenu :** Logo, Navigation principale, Groupes favoris, Profil

