## 13. PERFORMANCE & OPTIMISATION

### Images & Assets

**Format :** WebP avec fallback JPG/PNG  
**Lazy Loading :** Toutes images below-the-fold  
**Avatars :** Compression aggressive, taille max 200Ã—200px

### CSS

**Critical CSS :** Inline dans `<head>` pour first paint  
**CSS Modules :** Pour Ã©viter conflits de noms  
**Purge CSS :** Enlever classes inutilisÃ©es en production

### Animations

**GPU Acceleration :**

```css
.animated-element {
  will-change: transform;
  transform: translateZ(0);
}
```

**Reduce Motion :**

```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  * {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
  }
}
```

